      <scopecontent id="aspace_9848a36ea6715b13bfe93ec2c822293e">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The collection comprises designs, notes &amp; miscellaneous papers relating to buildings and agricultural improvements for Edgeworthstown, Richard Lovell Edgeworth's model village in Ireland, 1796-1815. Most of the designs and notes are by Daniel Augustus Beaufort, father in law of R.L. Edgeworth.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <userestrict id="aspace_477ae224ef367d5e34f582b30840794a">
